decoworld.model.world.combat.events

Class CollisionEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • decoworld.model.world.combat.events.CollisionEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CombatEvent

    public class CollisionEvent
extends java.lang.Object
implements CombatEvent
    Represents a collision event. Collision events are sent to objects that implement the HasCombat interface. In the event of a collision, two WorldItem's are involved. The source WorldItem corresponds to the object that is not receiving this event. The types of supported events are found in the CollisionEventType Enum.
